getManagedPageClass

protected abstract PageClass getManagedPageClass()
Returns the class of pages managed by this class implementation.

Returns:
PageClass.SPECIAL | PageClass.TEMPLATE | PageClass.ERROR | PageClass.DEFAULT. (DEFAULT represents DEFAULT AND MAIN, since both types are managed in the same widget).
Used for discriminatory grid refreshes.

onPageAdd

protected void onPageAdd(PageSelDTO ptDto)
Logic of this method is executed when controller fired a ADD event for the passed page.
The grid store is changed only if the passed page is managed by this widget (does nothing otherwise).
